  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC292">
        <l>ummun tāku miṭaṉumā ruṇṭē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/175/mode/1up">175</ref>.</p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC292-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘nīrkkōḻi kūppeyark kuntu’</l>
        <trailer>[puṟam - 395]</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu.
      </p>
      <p>
eṭṭu vakaippaṭṭa ummaiyum orummai eṉappaṭātu, viṉaicey maruṅkiṟ kālamoṭu vantatu.  (44)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tāmōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n227/mode/1up">224</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n228/mode/1up">225</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i – ḷ. 
viṉaiceyaṉmaruṅkiṟkālamoṭu varuvaṉavaṟṟuḷ ummīṟu untāyt tiritalumuṭaittu.
e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u – m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC292-Cena-cit1">
        <l>‘nīrkkōḻi kūppeyark kuntu.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC292-Cena-cit2">
        <l>‘nārari naṟaviṉāṇ makiḻtūṅkuntu.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m. varum.
      </p>
      <p>
viṉaiceyaṉmaruṅkiṟkālamoṭu varum ummeṉpatu ēṟpuḻikkōṭaleṉpataṉāṟ peṟṟām.
      </p>
      <p>
iṭaṉumāruṇṭēyeṉṟatu, ittiripu peyareccattiṟkīṟāyavaḻiyeṉpatu karutippōlum.
      </p>
      <p>
tammīṟu tiritaṉmutalāyiṉa ivvōttiṉuṭkūṟappaṭum iṭaiccoṟkēyeṉpatu itaṉāṉum peṟṟām. viṉaiyiyaluḷḷuṅ kūṟappaṭumāyiṉum, iṭaiccoṟṟiripākalāṉ īṇṭuk kūṟalum iyaipuṭaitteṉpatu.	(44)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/318/mode/1up">318</ref>.</p>
      <p>
um eṉpatu untu eṉattirital
      </p>
      <lg>
        <l>ummun tāku miṭaṉumā ruṇṭē.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
itu, ummeṉṉu miṭaiccoṟ ṟiriyu meṉkiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
        (i-ḷ) 
umun tāku miṭaṉumā ruṇṭē ― viṉaiceyaṉ maruṅkiṟ kālamoṭu varuvaṉavaṟṟuḷ um mīṟu untāyt tiritalu muṭaittueṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
(u-m)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC292-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>nīrkkōḻi kūppeyarkkuntu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC292-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>nārari naṟavi ṉāṉmakiḻ tūṅkuntu</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavarum.
      </p>
      <p>
iṭaṉumāruṇṭē yeṉṟataṉā ṉittiripu peyareccattiṟkē koḷka. <num xml:lang="en">(44)</num>
    </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n192/mode/1up">185</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n193/mode/1up">186</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvum atu.
      </p>
      <p>
        u-m:―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC292-Tey-cit1">
        <l>“nellariyu miruntoḻuvar,</l>
        <l>ceññāyiṟṟu veyiṉmuṉaiyiṟ,</l>
        <l>ṟeṇkaṭaṟṟirai micaippāyuntu,</l>
        <l>tiṇṭimil vaṉparatavar,</l>
        <l>veppuṭaiyamaṭṭuṇṭu,</l>
        <l>taṇkuravaic cīrtūṅkuntu,</l>
        <l>tūvaṟ kalitta tēmpāy puṉṉai,</l>
        <l>melliṇark kaṇṇi milainta maintar,</l>
        <l>elvaḷai makaḷir talaikkai tarūuntu,</l>
        <l>vaṇṭupaṭa malarnta taṇṇaṟuṅ kāṉaṉ,</l>
        <l>muṇṭakak kōtai yoṇṭoṭi makaḷir,</l>
        <l>irumpaṉaiyiṉ kurumpainīrum,</l>
        <l>pūṅkarumpiṉ ṟīñcāṟum,</l>
        <l>ōṅkumaṇaṟ kuvavuttāḻait,</l>
        <l>tīnīrō ṭuṭaṉvirāy,</l>
        <l>munnī ruṇṭu munnīrp pāyun,</l>
        <l>tāṅkā vuṟaiyu ṇallūr keḻīiya’</l>
        <trailer>(puṟam-24)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟavaḻi um untāyiṟṟu. eṇṇummai atikārappaṭṭu varutalāṉ, ivvāṟu varuvatu, ōr poruṇmēl ummai aṭukkiyavaḻi eṉṟu koḷka. īṇṭu eṇṇummai yāṅkateṉiṉ, oru poruṇmēl pala viṉaiccol varutaliṉ, avai oru mukattāṉ eṇṇappaṭṭavām.	[43]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
